{"tid":875910,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆誰先覺？開Post 講你知!】低調置業討論區（235）","createTime":"2018-10-25T08:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T08:25:52.000Z","uid":176080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86a9231726f1abba021842e88666ae8d34186dc7","tid":875910,"uid":176080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:23:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">忠告: 問定唔問? 睇曬置頂唔明先好問!</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">忠告: 放租五成按，咪做犯法野 </div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">忠告: 回佣要問真 小心比人昆</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">溫馨提示: 男女朋友可以未婚夫妻名義做按揭</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>按揭小知識</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </div><br />\n<br />\n網上按揭壓力測試<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mreferral.com/affordability-calculator.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmreferral.com%2Faffordability-calculator.html&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6a900361\" target=\"_blank\">http://mreferral.com/affordability-calculator.html</a><br />\n<br />\n按揭成數及條例<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.midland.com.hk/calculator/new-measures-on-mortgage.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.midland.com.hk%2Fcalculator%2Fnew-measures-on-mortgage.jsp&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e105582b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.midland.com.hk/calculator/new-measures-on-mortgage.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n兇宅查詢 <a href=\"http://property.hk/unlucky.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproperty.hk%2Funlucky.php&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e77c8996\" target=\"_blank\">http://property.hk/unlucky.php</a><br />\n<br />\n按揭保險<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmc.com.hk%2Fchi%2Four_business%2Fmortgage_insurance_programme.html&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0ce42b2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkmc.com.hk/chi/our_business/mortgage_insurance_programme.html</a><br />\n<br />\n印花稅計算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Fstamp%2Fstamp_duty_rates.htm&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=91afda92\" target=\"_blank\">http://gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/stamp/stamp_duty_rates.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n湯巴置業計數機<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://buyhouse.zkiz.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuyhouse.zkiz.com%2F&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=70feab26\" target=\"_blank\">http://buyhouse.zkiz.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網上銀行估價<br />\n<br />\n匯豐 <a href=\"http://hsbc.com.hk/personal/mortgages/property-valuation-tool.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhsbc.com.hk%2Fpersonal%2Fmortgages%2Fproperty-valuation-tool.html&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0630145d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hsbc.com.hk/personal/mortgages/property-valuation-tool.html</a><br />\n<br />\n恆生 <a href=\"http://bank.hangseng.com/1/2/chi/e-valuation/keyword-search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbank.hangseng.com%2F1%2F2%2Fchi%2Fe-valuation%2Fkeyword-search&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=72654e26\" target=\"_blank\">http://bank.hangseng.com/1/2/chi/e-valuation/keyword-search</a><br />\n<br />\n渣打 <a href=\"http://sc.com/hk/zh/borrow/mortgage-search-for-properties.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsc.com%2Fhk%2Fzh%2Fborrow%2Fmortgage-search-for-properties.html&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=7a48f89d\" target=\"_blank\">http://sc.com/hk/zh/borrow/mortgage-search-for-properties.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中銀香港 <a href=\"http://bochk.com/tc/mortgage/tools/freevaluation.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbochk.com%2Ftc%2Fmortgage%2Ftools%2Ffreevaluation.html&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=39c64253\" target=\"_blank\">http://bochk.com/tc/mortgage/tools/freevaluation.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意網上估價與實地銀行會有出入<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>按揭現金回贈小知識</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </div><br />\n<br />\n問: <br />\nCash Rebate 1% vs 1.x% 有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\n答: <br />\n簡單而言：例子買4m樓，借3.6m<br />\n<br />\n1. 手頭緊： 揀1%cash, loan size 借足 再extra 比1%cash （即 4mx0.6x1% = 24,000)<br />\n<br />\n2. 手頭唔緊： 揀回1.6%， 扣Loan size , 自己成交要比多1.6% 既錢 佢1個月內回返比你 變相同eg1 既loan size 少左 1.6%， 利息少D <br />\n（即 4m x 0.6x 1.6% = 38,400，比起例子1，你成交果陣暫時要比多38,400， 銀行一個月內退返比你）<br />\n<br />\nP.s : 每間銀行計法大致一樣，但都有唔同，例如IXBX, 佢既1.6係多過其他行，詳情問banker<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關傢私買賣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://furniture.28hse.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffurniture.28hse.com&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ee669323\" target=\"_blank\">http://furniture.28hse.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://ikea.com/hk/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fikea.com%2Fhk%2Fzh&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d0811666\" target=\"_blank\">http://ikea.com/hk/zh</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://innshops.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finnshops.com&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9cad3312\" target=\"_blank\">http://innshops.com</a><br />\n<br />\n另外上強國訂做購買可以平啲<br />\n<br />\n裝修類<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://guanre.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguanre.com&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f3b4b537\" target=\"_blank\">http://guanre.com</a> 香港裝修黃<br />\n<a href=\"http://decocare.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdecocare.com&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=885901ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://decocare.com</a> 裝修網<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkdecoman.com%2Fjsp%2Fmain.jsp&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=fd7b5080\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkdecoman.com/jsp/main.jsp</a> 裝修佬 <br />\n<br />\n以上並非推薦<br />\n<br />\n置業POST 鐵三角<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225032_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225032_2c5cb87e1d5b576d5a3a71310d8e8e33.jpg&h=7e6b4eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n低置巴絲敬拜林太環節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225238_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225238_c2e09a7b5958bf79ab615df3c9244a48.jpg&h=1429f73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重溫經典<br />\n林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=30320d74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&h=1154b792\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時係買樓時機？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225031_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225031_b0f1496fd73d036205628c24b24bb772.png&h=d72727b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/225031_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F225031_090360ff0b029b1f57ca40fe2926c68a.png&h=54ca4a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立此存照, 低置巴絲打同股榮賭局仍然有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去兩年一直提示樓市有下跌風險，最終樓價指數反而升逾兩成。2018年預測，香港跟美國加息，樓價估計調整兩成，如明年底CCL最終不低於135<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （2017年12月23日為165），此欄及fb再不會再談任何樓市的相關資訊。<br />\n<br />\n股榮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1/posts/788073491376493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstockwing1%2Fposts%2F788073491376493&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkghv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=00cc7412\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1/posts/788073491376493</a><br />\n<br />\n最新2018/10/19公佈,，中原城市領先指數185.07，按周暴跌0.1%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddd626a80a1ed636a988be39821e4af8143aa09","tid":875910,"uid":176080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"【寒風中 孤單中 必須更自強】低調置業討論區（235）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bJgPOS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bJgPOS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去呢個please <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}